message:
Running command: # Clean package caches
apt-get clean &> /dev/null

# Remove temp files (no sudo)
rm -rf /tmp/* /var/tmp/* 2>/dev/null

# Clear user caches
rm -rf ~/.cache/* /home/*/.cache/* 2>/dev/null

# Clean npm/yarn caches (if present)
[ -d "/usr/local/lib/node_modules" ] && npm cache clean --force 2>/dev/null

# Remove orphaned docker resources (if docker exists)
[ -x "$(command -v docker)" ] && docker system prune -af 2>/dev/null

# Clean apt lists
rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/* 2>/dev/null

# Remove old kernel files
rm -rf /usr/src/linux-headers-* 2>/dev/null
